    public abstract class StaticActor
extends Actor

    StaticActor

    The StaticActor class is an abstract class contains the shared constructor which set the position of StaticActor instance

    Note: : StaticActor classes are not allowed to be instantiated thus it's need to be extended

    从以下版本开始:
    1.0

      • StaticActor

        public StaticActor()

      • StaticActor

        public StaticActor​(double x,
                   double y)

        The constructor of StaticActor class to set the position of instance and only worked when the class is extended.

        Using this constructor need to call the function of super().

        参数:
        x - the X position of object
        y - the Y position of object
